body:
The Riot team cops a lot of flack, especially when there&#039;s connectivity issues or a glitch with a sale. But regardless, they keep swimming, working hard to keep us happy and League awesome. Wouldn&#039;t it be nice, just every once in a while, that we show them how much we love them?

If you&#039;ve had a Rioter be a real manitee and go out of their way to help ya, give them a thank here :)

Personally, i&#039;d like to give a shout out to Agent Mindstar, who&#039;s always got a quick response when there&#039;s a connection issue. Keep up the good work fam &lt;3 {{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}}

